-- World Bank’s IFC Lends $15 Million to Romania Banca Transilvania
-- B y   A n d r a   T i m u
-- 2012-10-04T14:19:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-04/world-bank-s-ifc-lends-15-million-to-romania-banca-transilvania.html
The World Bank’s International
Finance Corp. will lend $15 million to  Romania’s Banca
Transilvania SA (TLV)  to help boost credits to small- and medium-sized
enterprises and exporters, according to an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andra Timu in Bucharest at 
 atimu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
